oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Occurrence of insects in three everbearing strawberry cultivars in a polythene tunnel compared to an outdoor cultivation
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Lindqvist, Isa
Tuovinen, Tuomo
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Crop health, quality, protection
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An experiment was established at MTT in 2008, aiming to improve profitability of strawberry production using everbearing cultivars. The first area of interest was to monitor insect pests and pest related injuries on three everbearing cultivars.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: Lindqvist, Isa and Tuovinen, Tuomo (2009) Occurrence of insects in three everbearing strawberry cultivars in a polythene tunnel compared to an outdoor cultivation. In: NJF Report, Nordic Association of Agricultural Scientists, 5 (9), NJF Report, p. 14.
